nme.com/artists/dream">D:Ream</a> 、Goldie Live、Chris Stussy、Mall Grab、Enzo Siragusa Gok Wan、Desiree、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/logic1000">Logic1000、</a> Kurupt FM 等的表演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>已被​​确认成为今年夏天标志性金字塔舞台的主角，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a>将在周日的传奇时段表演。</p><p>酷玩乐队 (Coldplay) 和杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 的演出也将于本周在<a href="https://www.bbc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC.com</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-coldplay-and-dua-lipas-headline-sets-to-be-first-ever-streamed-globally-on-bbc-com-3768213">进行直播</a>，这也是该网站有史以来首次在全球范围内播出。</p><p>其他将于今年登台的艺人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip</a> 。</p><p>格拉斯顿伯里最近的其他消息显示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/emily-eavis-confirms-glastonbury-is-likely-to-take-a-year-off-in-2026-3764018">该音乐节可能会在 2026 年暂停一年</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emily-eavis">艾米丽·伊维斯 (Emily Eavis)</a>最近在 BBC 的<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sou